OL,3,CRapist dies at Bridgend's Parc Prison
OL,5,FA rapist has died while serving a 12-
OL,6,Fyear jail term at Bridgend's Parc
OL,7,Fprison.
OL,9,FJohn Hyde, 79, was sentenced in 2019
OL,10,Fafter being found guilty of historic
OL,11,Fsex offences.
OL,13,FIt means 13 Parc inmates have died
OL,14,Fsince late February.
OL,16,FUnlike some of the other cases, Hyde's
OL,17,Fdeath is not thought to be linked to a
OL,18,Fdrug overdose or self-harm.
