OL,3,CRapist dies at Bridgend's Parc Prison
OL,5,FIt's understood Hyde, who died in the
OL,6,Fjail on July 26, was receiving
OL,7,Fpalliative care and a do-not-
OL,8,Fresuscitate order was in place.
OL,10,FA spokeswoman for G4S ` the private
OL,11,Fsecurity giant which runs the jail `
OL,12,Fsaid: "As with all deaths in custody,
OL,13,Fthis will be investigated by the
OL,14,Fprisons and probation ombudsman, and
OL,15,Fthe cause of death is for the coroner
OL,16,Fto determine."
