OL,3,CRapist dies at Bridgend's Parc Prison
OL,5,FHyde, who lived in Ethel Street in
OL,6,FCanton, Cardiff, was jailed in January
OL,7,F2019 for 12 years and four months
OL,8,Fafter being convicted of sexual abuse
OL,9,Fwhich took place in the 1980s and
OL,10,F1990s.
OL,12,FHe was found guilty of two counts of
OL,13,Frape and he pleaded guilty to two
OL,14,Fattempts at perverting the course of
OL,15,Fjustice.
OL,17,FIn June, G4S replaced the director of
OL,18,FParc by mutual agreement following
OL,19,Fdisorder at the jail and a string of
OL,20,Finmate fatalities.
